text: Lüterkofen-Ichertswil is a municipality of the Bucheggberg district in the canton of Solothurn in Switzerland. It was created in 1961 from the merger of the two independent municipalities of Lüterkofen and Ichertswil. == References == == Other websites == * Official website * * Category:Municipalities in Bucheggberg District
